  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize marker acquisition: switch to marker_track as soon as marker_seen occurs.",
    "In marker_track, move_to_marker is the only controllable; if marker_lost, initiate scan_full to reacquire.",
    "On marker_close, always transition to goal_stop and only allow stop.",
    "After each forward_commit, require a scan_full to prevent long blind runs.",
    "After obstacle_front, require recovery (move_backward) and a scan before resuming exploration.",
    "obs_left always prefers rotate_clockwise; obs_right always prefers rotate_counterclockwise to avoid oscillation.",
    "All uncontrollable events are total; only one controllable per state (except obs_front for recovery).",
    "No infinite controllable loops; all commit/scan/recover states are one-shot.",
    "Exploration alternates between short forward moves and scans until marker is seen.",
    "Obstacle recovery always passes through a scan before resuming forward movement."
  ]
